---
title: Spanish-Style Tapas with Beef Albondigas Enjoy a multi-dish culinary tour of a new destination!
description: Our collection of Spain’s famously shareable tapas dishes makes a perfect festive meal at home. Beef meatballs with savory romesco sauce, garlic-paprika shrimp, and salty prosciutto are joined by creamy ricotta with fig jam, fresh tomato sauce, and golden brown crostini made to scoop up every last bite—no passport required!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67ceb3f56a498293bec85b0e-f7130eff.jpeg
